ey Components#W&B Models#{3}":[33,34],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used":[35,43],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{1}":[37,37],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{2}":[38,38],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{3}":[39,39],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{4}":[40,40],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{5}":[41,41],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{6}":[42,43],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models":[44,51],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{1}":[46,46],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{2}":[47,47],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{3}":[48,48],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{4}":[49,49],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{5}":[50,51],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#System Requirements":[52,61],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#System Requirements#{1}":[54,61],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack":[62,71],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{1}":[64,64],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{2}":[65,65],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{3}":[66,66],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{4}":[67,67],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{5}":[68,68],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{6}":[69,69],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{7}":[70,71],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related":[72,80],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related#{1}":[74,74],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related#{2}":[75,75],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related#{3}":[76,77],"#AI Observability for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related#{4}":[78,80]},"outlinks":[{"title":"NVIDIA AI Blueprint for building data flywheels","target":"to demonstrate how observability and experiment tracking can be added to agentic AI workflows.\n\n## Overview\n\n[W&B Weave]( enhances the NVIDIA AI Blueprint for building data flywheels by providing advanced traceability for continuous model optimization with real-world data and user feedback. While the blueprint orchestrates automated evaluation and selection of models for optimal latency, cost, and enterprise-grade accuracy, Weights & Biases layers in native traceability, robust experiment tracking, version management, and visualization.\n\n## Key Components\n\n### W&B Weave\n- Evaluate, monitor, and iterate on AI applications\n- Continuous improvement in quality, latency, cost, and safety\n- Comprehensive evaluations with new models\n- Debugging and production monitoring\n- Secure collaboration\n\n### W&B Models\n- Train, fine-tune, govern, and manage models\n- Experiment speed and team collaboration\n- Performance, data reliability, and security\n\n## NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used\n\n- **NeMo Customizer**: Model finetuning\n- **NeMo Evaluator**: Model and workflow evaluation\n- **Datastore**: Stores datasets, evaluation results, fine-tuning artifacts\n- **Deployment Manager**: Deploys and experiments with candidate models\n- **Entity Store**: Unified data model and registry\n- **NIM Proxy**: Routes inference across multiple models\n\n## NIM Models\n\n- llama-3.3-70b-instruct\n- llama-3.2-1b-instruct\n- llama-3.2-3b-instruct\n- llama-3.1-70b-instruct\n- llama-3.1-8b-instruct\n\n## System Requirements\n\n| Component | Requirement |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| Hardware (Self-hosted LLM Judge","line":15},{"title":"ai-orchestration-for-data-flywheel-by-iguazio","target":"ai-orchestration-for-data-flywheel-by-iguazio","line":74},{"title":"rag-concept","target":"rag-concept","line":75},{"title":"cyborg-enterprise-rag-blueprint","target":"cyborg-enterprise-rag-blueprint","line":76}],"metadata":{"created":"2026-04-05","tags":["#rag","#ai-observability","#data-flywheel","#nvidia-blueprint","#weights-biases"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:WIKI/raw/ai-observability-for-data-flywheel-by-weights-biases.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"u4znsp","at":1776764153483},"key":"WIKI/raw/ai-observability-for-data-flywheel-by-weights-biases.md#---frontmatter---","lines":[1,9],"size":130,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
